    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-安装"><a href="#1-安装" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装"></a>1. 安装</h1><h2 id="1-1-依赖安装"><a href="#1-1-依赖安装" class="headerlink" title="1.1 依赖安装"></a>1.1 依赖安装</h2><ul>
<li><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git</a> </li>
<li><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">node.js</a> </li>
</ul>
<h2 id="1-2-安装hexo"><a href="#1-2-安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.2 安装hexo"></a>1.2 安装hexo</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="1-3-生成博客系统"><a href="#1-3-生成博客系统" class="headerlink" title="1.3 生成博客系统"></a>1.3 生成博客系统</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">cd &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<a id="more"></a>

<blockquote>
<p>hexo常用命令</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="1-4-部署"><a href="#1-4-部署" class="headerlink" title="1.4 部署"></a>1.4 部署</h2><h3 id="1-4-1-命令式简单快速的方法"><a href="#1-4-1-命令式简单快速的方法" class="headerlink" title="1.4.1 命令式简单快速的方法"></a>1.4.1 命令式简单快速的方法</h3><ul>
<li><p>登录 <code>github</code>，创建 <code>&lt;username&gt;.github.io</code> 仓库</p>
</li>
<li><p>编辑站点配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> ，编辑后内容如下</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    repo:</span> <span class="attr">https://github.com/&lt;user_name&gt;/&lt;user_name&gt;.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">    branch:</span> <span class="string">&lt;branch&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>用hexo命令一键发布</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="2-简单配置"><a href="#2-简单配置" class="headerlink" title="2. 简单配置"></a>2. 简单配置</h1><h1 id="3-高级配置"><a href="#3-高级配置" class="headerlink" title="3. 高级配置"></a>3. 高级配置</h1>]]></content>
